Merc Soldier
The Merc Soldier is a professional military contractor: solid combat skills,
reliable under fire, and loyal to their employer. Not as specialised as a
Headhunter or Special Forces, but flexible and widely employable.

Merc Soldiers have the most secondary skill picks of any combat OCC, allowing
them to tailor their capabilities to their preferred style. They choose from
Military, Physical, Espionage, Pilot, Technical, and W.P. categories.

Attribute requirements: PS 9, PE 9.
Starting equipment: Body armour, two ranged weapons, combat knife, radio,
and mercenary contracts or unit affiliation.
